                                                    <tr class="background_color" style="height: 45px;">
                                                        <td>
                                                            <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lbl_philosophy_title" class="index_header_title">教育理念及校訓</span>
                                                        </td>       
                                                    </tr>
                                                    <tr style="height: 264px;">
                                                        <td class="auto-style1" style="background-color: #E3ECBE;">
                                                            <div>
                                                                <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lbl_philosophy" class="lbl_philosophy"><p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span style="text-align: justify; font-size: 20px;"><strong>本校的課程以兒童為本，<br />
</strong></span><strong><span style="text-align: justify;">培育兒童</span><span style="text-align: justify; color: #ff0000;">德</span><span style="text-align: justify;">、</span><span style="text-align: justify; color: #e36c09;">智</span><span style="text-align: justify;">、</span><span style="text-align: justify; color: #76923c;">體</span><span style="text-align: justify;">、</span><span style="text-align: justify; color: #00b0f0;">群</span><span style="text-align: justify;">、</span><span style="text-align: justify; color: #0070c0;">美</span><span style="text-align: justify;">、</span><span style="text-align: justify; color: #7030a0;">靈<br />
</span><span style="text-align: justify;">六育均衡發展。</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>
<span style="text-align: justify;">除主題教學法外，並融入兒童設計活動，<br />
啟動幼兒創意思考及培育多元智能的發展。<br />
</span>
<br />
<span style="text-align: justify;">校訓：我們要彼此相愛</span></strong></span></p></span>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </td>
                                                    </tr>
                                                </table>                                           
                                            
										</div><div id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lc_right_col" class="t-col t-col-6 t-col-xs-12 t-col-sm-12 t-col-md-6 RightIndex">
											
                                                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                                                    <tr class="background_color" style="height: 45px;">                                                        
                                                        <td>
                                                            <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lbl_news_title" class="index_header_title">News</span>
                                                        </td>
                                                    </tr>
                                                    <tr style="height: 264px;">                                                        
                                                        <td valign="top" style="background-color: #f1f9e4;">
                                                            <div>
